sequenceDiagram
    participant SDK as MLflow SDK<br/>(Notebook Pod)
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as ODH Data Science Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over SDK,S3: Flow 1: SDK Client Experiment Tracking

    SDK->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>HTTP/5000
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorized (mlflow.kubeflow.org)
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run metadata<br/>DB credentials
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>AWS credentials
    S3-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 JSON Response
    Gateway-->>SDK: 200 JSON Response

    Note over SDK,S3: Flow 2: UI Access via Gateway

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/<br/>Auth: OpenShift OAuth Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>HTTP/5000
    MLflow-->>Gateway: React UI HTML/JS
    Gateway-->>Browser: React UI
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/ajax-api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments<br/>DB credentials
    PG-->>MLflow: Result set
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 JSON
    Gateway-->>Browser: 200 JSON

    Note over SDK,S3: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    SDK->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>OTLP/HTTP protobuf<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>DB credentials
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>SDK: 200 OK
